3. Confirm your diff since HEAD touches only `schedule/__init__.py` and `test_schedule.py` (no other files).

Report `PASS` in your final reply with file:line evidence once both checks are green. Report `BLOCKED` if you believe this fix is wrong or cannot be made this way.
